                        participating in the regridding operation are
                        optionally returned into 'srcFracField' and
                        'dstFracField'.\n
        Arguments:\n
            :RETURN: ESMP_RouteHandle           :: routehandle\n
            ESMP_Field                          :: srcField\n
            ESMP_Field                          :: dstField\n
